@startuml
actor Student
participant Browser
participant "EduSecure API" as API
participant Lecturer

Student -> Browser : upload assignment file
Browser -> API : send file without hash/signature
API --> Lecturer : make file available
Lecturer -> Lecturer : cannot verify authorship or tampering

note right of API
The system has no cryptographic proof
that the file is original or untampered.
end note
@enduml

